                "key_steps": [
                  "1. 正弦定理：$\\frac{a}{\\sin A} = \\frac{b}{\\sin B} = \\frac{c}{\\sin C} = 2R$。",
                  "   $2R = \\frac{2}{\\sin(\\pi/3)} = \\frac{4}{\\sqrt{3}}$。",
                  "2. 表达 $b, c$：",
                  "   $b = \\frac{4}{\\sqrt{3}} \\sin B$。",
                  "   $c = \\frac{4}{\\sqrt{3}} \\sin C = \\frac{4}{\\sqrt{3}} \\sin(\\frac{2\\pi}{3} - B)$。",
                  "3. 构建周长函数：",
                  "   $L = 2 + \\frac{4}{\\sqrt{3}} [\\sin B + \\sin(\\frac{2\\pi}{3} - B)]$。",
                  "4. 三角恒等变换（辅助角）：",
                  "   $\\sin B + \\sin(\\frac{2\\pi}{3} - B) = \\sin B + \\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{2}\\cos B + \\frac{1}{2}\\sin B = \\frac{3}{2}\\sin B + \\frac{\\sqrt{3}}{2}\\cos B$",
